title: ETNIES PRESENTS THE FRONT GIRLS AT HEVY 2011: EPISODE 3
description: With the little English town of Lympne back to its normal quiet life after a full on weekend of Punkrock, etnies takes you one last time to Hevy 2011. Experience 3 days of punk, beer, “roly polies” and sunshine at Hevy 2011 and see Front girl Lauren shoot some quick fire questions at “Your Demise” and “Four Year Strong”.
